{"tid":381583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★垃圾郵件機器人意外洩露 7 億電郵密碼","createTime":"2017-08-31T05:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T08:59:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecfc3f37e900cf7dc43e0bec3f77afb384d73d17","tid":381583,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"有系統保安專家 Troy Hunt 在他的網站透露有垃圾郵件機器人不慎洩露高達 7.11 億個電郵地址和密碼，規模大得不能想像。會洩漏的原因是因為一台設定不良的伺服器被有心人成功駭入，然後將個人資料洩露出去，這 7.11 億個電郵帳號也可能重覆了過去其他洩漏事件中搜尋回來的。利用上述電郵和密碼，垃圾郵件機器人向其他人寄送垃圾郵件，令你防不勝防。<br />\n<br />\n面對這次洩漏，我們只有一個方法可以防止垃圾郵件機器人冒充你發送電郵，就是轉換密碼，而且今次洩漏有關數據已被完整上載到一個網頁（按這裡<a href=\"https://haveibeenpwned.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhaveibeenpwned.com%2F&d=95kRaKE2A%2FWIR7VeuoWqUp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7a629386\" target=\"_blank\">https://haveibeenpwned.com/</a>），你可以輸入的電郵看看你在某討論區的密碼是否被洩漏了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/08/31/700-million-email-and-passwords-leaked/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F700-million-email-and-passwords-leaked%2F&d=95kRaKE2A%2FWIR7VeuoWqUp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=cd319b82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/08/31/700-million-email-and-passwords-leaked/</a>"},{"pid":"ebc2a06b6e2832c76f0ac723b462bb74dac38256","tid":381583,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08ed2bbfc132c55e8fdf4efbc66508aec2d67d6","tid":381583,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"見到自己"},{"pid":"4549b8bc30a3efc6d68d18903a870e8c239b49eb","tid":381583,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"